com.camerontec.catalys.core.exception

Class CatalysException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • com.camerontec.catalys.core.exception.CatalysException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BadDataExceptionWithCode, CryptoException, LogonException, MessageException, ProtocolException, RoutingException, ScpException, TimedoutException

    public class CatalysException
extends Exception
    This is the base class for a number of Catalys exceptions.

    Each exception has the following attributes:

    • Code - Integer constant indicating the type of exception. Constants for all codes are declared below as constants starting with "EX_".
    • Data - Any object may be associated with the exception.
    • Nested - A nested exception.
    See Also:
